    "On the other hand, experimental group students received the same education except for the writing section, which was expanded with PBL.",
    "When it was the time to write, they gathered, defined the problem and came up with lasting solutions collaboratively.",
    "After that, they wrote the reflection to illustrate all stages which increased their productivity and accountability.",
    "Subsequently, each student wrote a novel essay about the given topic.",
    "It is essential to emphasize that a hybrid writing mode was employed in the experimental group, which was flexible to write on paper or send their essays electronically via features of Microsoft Forms."
